  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803640/extras/df9f25e92349910768edf5c8ad567da5.poster.avif?t=1715590219\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803640/extras/df9f25e92349910768edf5c8ad567da5.webm?t=1715590219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803640/extras/df9f25e92349910768edf5c8ad567da5.mp4?t=1715590219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>ONE WAY<br>The game ONE WAY will tell about the adventures of the main character, who will fight off opponents, solve puzzles, avoid traps and look for the main boss who betrayed the main character in the past.<br>Key Features:<br>- Puzzles and traps<br>- Interesting and energetic gameplay<br>- Different levels<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803640/extras/27349991ade8537fd8c0cd75ca4888e7.poster.avif?t=1715590219\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803640/extras/27349991ade8537fd8c0cd75ca4888e7.webm?t=1715590219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1803640/extras/27349991ade8537fd8c0cd75ca4888e7.mp4?t=1715590219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A real platformer with voxel graphics, in which you will find everything - difficult levels, pleasant voxel 3D graphics, traps, various enemies",
